The US Air Force flew two reconnaissance missions over eastern Ukraine this week, the first on December 27 just a few days after Russia said it would withdraw 10,000 troops from the shared border, CNN reported.

- Ukraine has been a point of contention for the two countries since the annexation of Crimea in 2014, Al Jazeera reports
